&lt;p&gt;This is a remote, part-time role with the ability to evolve into a full time role. We would prefer a minimum of 10 hours a week, though week to week availability is flexible.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rate: $125/hour.&lt;/p&gt;
